gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Wizards 118, Spurs 113
gameRecap.excerpt: The Wizards defeated the Spurs, 118-113. Kyle Kuzma recorded 18 points, 11 rebounds, and five assists for the Wizards, with Daniel Gafford adding 16 points and 13 rebounds in the victory. Victor Wembanyama tallied 22 points, 11 rebounds, and three blocks for the Spurs in the losing effort. The Wizards improve to 9-37, while the Spurs fall to 10-37.
